      <title>欧盟国家举行会谈，讨论放宽天然气储存目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/group-of-eu-countries-hold-talks-on-relaxing-gas-storage-targets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心高昂的天然气价格会导致储存天然气无利可图，一些拥有该地区最大天然气储备的欧洲国家已举行了早期非正式会谈，商讨在 2025 年之后放宽补充目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/group-of-eu-countries-hold-talks-on-relaxing-gas-storage-targets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 17:08:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国对美国石油征收关税之际，美国石油出口已从峰值下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/china-tariffs-on-us-oil-come-as-exports-have-slumped-from-peak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国针对美国石油实施的第一轮制裁并未引起太大反响，交易员们猜测此举不太可能影响美国原油出口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/china-tariffs-on-us-oil-come-as-exports-have-slumped-from-peak</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 17:00:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>皇家加勒比邮轮获标普高等级信用评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/royal-caribbean-snags-high-grade-credit-rating-from-s-p</link>
      <description><![CDATA[皇家加勒比游轮有限公司 (Royal Caribbean Cruises Ltd.) 在标准普尔全球评级中恢复投资级评级，几天前这家游轮运营商创下了最繁忙预订期的开局记录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/royal-caribbean-snags-high-grade-credit-rating-from-s-p</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 16:48:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税之争巩固了美国优异表现：瑞士宝盛集团</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-04/tariff-debate-reinforces-us-outperformance-do-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Julius Baer 投资组合经理 An Do 表示，关税辩论强化了她对美国表现优异的信心，因为美国有大量长期增长故事，可以免受波动的影响。她在“开盘交易”节目中与彭博社的 Anna Edwards 和 Guy Johnson 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-04/tariff-debate-reinforces-us-outperformance-do-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 16:46:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>咖啡价格有望因供应问题创下 45 年来最长涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/coffee-set-for-longest-gaining-streak-in-45-years-on-supply-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场正在努力解决主要种植区持续存在的供应问题，咖啡价格有望创下 1980 年以来最长的上涨势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/coffee-set-for-longest-gaining-streak-in-45-years-on-supply-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 12:39:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰晤士水务公司首席财务官认为顾问费将突破 2 亿英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/thames-water-adviser-fees-could-breach-200-million-cfo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰晤士水务公司很可能在今年年中之前向顾问支付约 2 亿英镑（2.5 亿美元），因为该公司希望找到股权投资者并削减负债。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/thames-water-adviser-fees-could-breach-200-million-cfo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 11:40:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
