      <title>特朗普暂停贸易关税给新兴市场带来喘息机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-s-trade-tariffs-pause-offers-breather-to-emerging-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们对特朗普总统的威胁可能引发全面贸易战的担忧有所缓解，新兴市场股票和货币周二出现上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-s-trade-tariffs-pause-offers-breather-to-emerging-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 11:20:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中美贸易战冲击美元走低 铜价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/copper-and-zinc-climb-as-trump-delays-tariffs-on-canada-mexico</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对中国商品征收 10% 的关税，而北京方面也采取了一系列措施予以回应，美元走低导致铜价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/copper-and-zinc-climb-as-trump-delays-tariffs-on-canada-mexico</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 01:25:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普准备加大对伊朗的压力，油价缩减跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国总统唐纳德·特朗普准备加强对伊朗的制裁，可能威胁到该国的原油出口，油价缩减跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 23:35:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
